{"tid":19741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府發千字文稱無政治考慮","createTime":"2016-12-03T03:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T08:25:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6198471065dcb00c6bf8bdc020a7da702c8e6acf","tid":19741,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19853696&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19853696%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161203&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9d628d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19853696%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161203&h=dd9a71c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19853696&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161203</a><br />\n<br />\n政府發千字文稱無政治考慮<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長袁國<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今屆立法會除了梁、游的宣誓出事外，另有3名議員也要進行第二次宣誓，當中包括讀錯誓詞、講漏「香港」兩字變成「定當擁護中華人民共和國特別行政區《基本法》」的黃定光，但政府只對其餘二人劉小麗及姚松炎採取行動。政府昨傍晚發新聞稿強調，今次出手沒有政治考慮。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨傍晚發千字文新聞稿解釋，稱參考了原訟庭法官區慶祥判詞，並外聘獨立資深大律師給予法律意見後，決定只入稟要求法官裁定該4人宣誓無效；又強調今次出手純屬法律及執法決定，沒有政治考慮。律政司司長袁國強昨晚亦重申，政府入稟絕非為推翻選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n近日不少市民如學生莫嘉傑及由「愛港之聲」高達斌陪同的翠華餐廳侍應陳嘉偉等，入稟要求法庭取消多名非建制派議員議席。政府在新聞稿中特別提到這一點，解釋政府不適宜以「有利害關係的一方」（interested party）身份，參與在市民提出的司法覆核案件中，認為此類涉及重大公眾利益的訴訟應由政府進行；又稱如政府非申請人，或者無權在官司上作決定，情況並不理想。<br />\n<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;民主派恐失分組點票否決權<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;中央示好　梁即倒米"},{"pid":"65401fab99c0553b42da2666225d65bb7c253825","tid":19741,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"7df0ac9e88075ae25cab610202a5d4e53e11be88","tid":19741,"uid":3383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac55276cd8aeb694cc76bcda4cb3254890d848d","tid":19741,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愈描愈黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6516d7659a4edd73b84719a103cc22469fc97894","tid":19741,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"無政治考慮有政治任務姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79421afe738df8724e39320879857e8545f5d0f7","tid":19741,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209ac259c631fa3f36b28d9160d218f1e15f96d7","tid":19741,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"請問乜撚嘢叫純粹法律決定， 咁你都要有個目的去用法律決定， 唔通透過法律達到你嘅法律決定， 講唔通嘛， 咪撚詭辯啦好心， 全香港白痴都知係政治目的啦， 認咗佢仲冇咁肉酸， 法律目的？ 自欺欺人， 指鹿為馬， 可笑可笑， 垃圾語言偽術， 不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"a62e3ea353385c850045e7dd872144af7cfbb398","tid":19741,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"搵鬼信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c5b971d5e936bb002e5a8fa51cbacfc8dd61eb","tid":19741,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愈描愈黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a620a1b6f855a51eb8c95b0f08186e1a620324","tid":19741,"uid":4722,"like":0,"dislike":